@startuml TEDE_Maintenance_Request
autonumber

actor Customer

participant "Technnet Connect"

participant "Technnet Maintenance"

participant Technician

participant Inventory

participant "Technnet Insight"

database Database

Customer -> "Technnet Connect" : Submit maintenance request

"Technnet Connect" -> "Technnet Maintenance" : Create work order

"Technnet Maintenance" -> Technician : Assign technician

Technician -> "Technnet Maintenance" : Accept assignment

Technician -> Inventory : Request spare parts

Inventory --> Technician : Issue parts

Technician -> "Technnet Maintenance" : Upload inspection report

"Technnet Maintenance" -> Database : Save report

"Technnet Maintenance" -> "Technnet Insight" : Update KPIs

@enduml